Class LoginLogoutSystem

  • Object
    • LoginLogoutSystem

  • public class LoginLogoutSystem
extends Object
    This class will determine what is the current user that is logged in. It can also log in an user, if no user is currently logged in. It can also log out the current user. Created by Alexis Tinoco (March 15, 2018 @ 3:30) Modified: David Wang
